column5: All geared up and ready for tomorrow! Gonna hit some walleye and bass action with this cold front. Ill do my best to film some big old sturgeon jumpin for the good folks here! Sitting on the deck now and not hearing much? Maybe the cold front turns them off jumping? But I'll give her a shot!
they would be great to record
Looking forward to seeing what you can get. Lots jumping around here but I haven't the patience to film.
I look forward to seeing that.
Had a good day fishing but it was slow. Caught a good mixed bag of walleye, pike and bass. Got a ton of sturgeon footy too  now I just gotta edit it...
Come on. What am I going to watch while drinking my coffee?
